Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge town!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place used to be full of pirates\Non their way to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get some equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can get some nice\Ningredients in a town this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice women, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got something I wanna buy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How're you gonna do that, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright! I'm gonna check\Nout the execution platform!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Die!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Glasses... Glasses...\N--Hey. Are these them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay me back for those!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing! Do you know how\Nto get to the execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a toast!\NTo the Eternal King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Eternal King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where the\Ngreatest pirate in history died...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the place where\Nthe pirate age began...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna see the view the King\Nof the Pirates saw before he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Time to go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kitetsu III and Yubashiri! Zoro's New\NSwords and the Woman Sergeant Major"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!\NWhere are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The execution platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the place where\Nthe King of the Pirates died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Monkey D. Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can mobilize\N100 men immediately, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the entire battalion afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more than enough on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?\NI'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the guy with the\Nbiggest bounty in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy. Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Smoker of the Navy.\NI'm in charge of Loguetown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Arrest? Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just about to go into the Grand\NLine and be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to get arrested\Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll have to beat me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get into the Grand\NLine unless you can beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the rule of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's assuming you're brave\Nenough to fight me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get into the Grand\NLine unless I beat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's made out of rubber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! My legs are tangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this 'cause\NI wanna! It's my legs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unstuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as pathetic as you,\Nworth 30 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even need to use\Nmy Devil Fruit power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fists are more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,22 years ago, I saw his execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His proud final moments were\Nworthy of the King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, King of the Pirates?\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even enter the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in getting back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to\Nknow that unless I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really messed that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are,\Nmy beloved mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My damn mistake.\NPlease come again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, was she beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! I'll take this, too!\N--Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. The cards say that\Ndetestable runt is already in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time for revenge\Nhas flashily come at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Do you successfully take his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who dies is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! W-We just saw--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure flew a long way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll sleep for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, are you okay?\N--Do you suppose he's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.\NI'll pay you back... somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like you\Nwould have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about you just seems off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-True, I don't have any money, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those wrinkles between your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That look of having\Neaten nothing for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a sick mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your wife run out on you and\Nleave you with five babies to nurse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask for details!\NJust come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:09:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cleaning man just quit his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you work for the navy, you'll\Nnever need to worry about money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very lucky person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! Why should\NI work for the navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to run off?!\NYou're insulting a person's kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your poor spirit's more of\Nan issue than your money problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major! It's time for training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! Please work hard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a lot!\NMaybe I'll hit another store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, how'd I get stuck doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's... working for the navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend you didn't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\NI'm gettin' nowhere like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess even three brushes is best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! You are Pirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you in here cleaning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intel has it you've teamed up\Nwith Monkey D. Luffy's crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems someone attacked them!\NThere's no trace of whoever did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For your glasses."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that freaked me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She looks\Nway too much like Kuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention she's\Na swordsman, of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world sure is a big place.\NBut I doubt I'll ever see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like some swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes! Welcome!\NHave a look at anything you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our shop's been in business\Nfor 200 years, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got 100,000 Berries.\NSell me two swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Two swords for 100,000 Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he has no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50,000 a sword'll only\Nget you some dull blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make do with whatever.\NI just don't got any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make do with whatever?\NHmph! What an amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sword on his waist!\NCould it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, h-h-hold on. L-L-Lemme\Nsee that sword of y-y-yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you all fidgety for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This really is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down! This is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An absolute amateur waltzed\Nright in here with a legendary sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's not a bad sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? I'll buy this\Nfrom you for 200,000 Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll have 300,000 Berries total!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could get three good\Nswords at 100,000 apiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Alright! I-I can make it\N250,000! No, 300,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Raise the price all\Nyou want, this sword isn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! I'll buy it\Nfrom you for 650,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you damn professional!\NHow does 800,000 Berries sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish polishing my Shigure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone went on a rampage\Nat the navy outpost earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were gone too, so I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's a royal-class dimwit...\N--Thank goodness! What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that you're\Nhere safe and sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...means you actually scoffed\Nat my kindness and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept money from\Nsomeone who's heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:14:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I bought some new glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this sword the Wado Ichimonji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the Wado Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it! Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful straight temper line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's one of the 21\NO-Wazamono swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! Look at this! It's worth\Nno less than 10 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing\Nwith such a legendary sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! You just\Nhad to blurt it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suing for obstruction of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Obstruction of business?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here for your Shigure,\Nright?! I'm done polishing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it and get the hell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you run straight into those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumb girl saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, that sword's\Nso legendary it'd be a waste
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a guy who doesn't know\Nits value to walk around with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the swords in that barrel\Nare 50,000 Berries apiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take whatever two you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really like swords,\Ncarrying three of them around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost like this one\Nbounty hunter out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bounty hunter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's famous! His name is Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the name a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's a famous swordsman\Nall throughout the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's a notorious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using swords as bounty-hunting\Ntools is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is evil so strong in this era?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the famous sword masters\Nare pirates or bounty hunters...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And almost all of the world's\Nlegendary swords are in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, maybe everyone has\Ntheir own circumstances and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All jobs need to keep up\Nwith the times somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, with my Shigure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to polish\Nmy skills as a swordsman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday gather\Nall the legendary swords
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are in the hands of\Ncriminals throughout the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 21 Top O-Wazamonos,\Nthe 21 O-Wazamonos,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the 50 Ryo-Wazamonos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll risk my life for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna take this sword, too?\NThe Wado Ichimonji, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that I want\Nlegendary swords...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying I don't like\Nthem being in criminals' hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sword! I think it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so! Kitetsu III!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Kitetsu III!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its predecessor, the Kitetsu II,\Nis an O-Wazamono sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Kitetsu I before that is\Nlisted as a Top O-Wazamono sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Is this sword\Nreally 50,000 Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! It's a respectable\NWazamono, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one! You have to choose that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It normally goes for one million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You absolutely have to choose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I can't sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Selling this for\N50,000 Berries is clearly strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cursed sword, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can just tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with the very first one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the Kitetsu have been superior\Nswords, but every last one is cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many famous master\Nswordsmen have met tragic deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after taking up Kitetsu swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, there ain't a single\Nperson who uses a Kitetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you'll leave this world\Neven if you use them unknowingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I wanna get rid of that thing,\Nbut I'm afraid it'll curse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I had no idea it\Nwas such a terrifying sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've minded my own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you a fool?! I can't sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die because of it, then\Nit'd be like I killed you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the fool!\NJust sell the stupid thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My luck, and this thing's curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see which one's stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Its sharpness is the real deal!\NIt'll take your whole arm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Could you choose me another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The make is black lacquer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the blade's\Ntemper pattern uneven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ryo-Wazamono "Yubashiri"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shop may not be much,\Nbut this is the finest sword I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't buy that. I already\Ntold you, I got no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the money. And I don't\Nneed any for the Kitetsu, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for trying to cheat you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've\Nseen a good swordsman's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the sword chooses the owner.\NI pray for your good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely feel more\Nrelaxed with three swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a big skinflint like\Nyou gave the family treasure away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with one man\Nentrusting a dream to another?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take out the damn trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so frightened...\Nthat I still can't stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Time to go\Nto the execution platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Found him?!\N--No, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was\NStraw Hat you saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We're sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Scour the place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, where is the execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bastard hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That way.\N--Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find Luffy! He's gotta be hiding\Nsomewhere in Loguetown still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have\Nto tell you not to shout?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm around,\Nhe'll show up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!\NDid something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi! Where the hell'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain! We have news!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you guys! Thank goodness!\NYou're conscious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were attacked by Zoro,\Nthe pirate hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he attack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make it to the\Nexecution platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get another look at\Nthe view the King of the Pirates saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Usopp's\Ngonna be in a showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he crazy?! There's no way\Nhe can beat him! He'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest gunslinger\Nbounty hunter there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Must be thanks\Nto the wanted poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Usopp! Where are you\Ngoing with all that stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usopp vs. Daddy the Parent;\NShowdown at High Noon"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
